o compare reality with fiction.\n\n# DISCOVER INVENTIONS\nOnce you unlock all 8 boxes of a Level Pack, you can compose a puzzle and discover a brief history of an invention.\n\nIt's not always easy to escape the room, so use all your IQ to crack the riddles. There's a logic behind all of them, even where it seems it's not!\n\n# IMMERSIVE SOUNDTRACK\nPlay the game with your headphones to get immersed in this amazing adventure.\n\n# HINTS\nGot stuck on some enigma? No worries, you can still get a helpful hint! You can also get in touch with me in case you really can't make it through a riddle, I'll be glad to help ;)\n\n# MULTILANGUAGE\nAvailable in English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Russian, and Japanese.\n\nThe game language will change automatically based on the language settings of your device", "short_description": "A VR escape room game where you have to solve intriguing riddles to open boxes and discover nice stories about popular inventions!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "$R36BSY5.png", "id": "3678762505771822", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031430_3678762509105155_2151975047074617165_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rBATWQzx-98Q7kNvgFYJ4H1&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCodAyc_zqo1JHFfrT-Xv2Bf73s9XWtI0z1JJyAldIgUw&oe=6777C865"}, {"file_name": "$R81V725.png", "id": "2720695481426567", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75262743_2720695484759900_604086922326600035_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=J6VtsuJcIU8Q7kNvgEIBtmI&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDlHOD9C-dj1FFLQaxQbX6iMkH8ax3CKesbWR-JaV24gQ&oe=6777C74D"}, {"file_name": "$RQ3SN6U.png", "id": "1552311425628973", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982519_1552311428962306_1218130395049083834_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6